<div class="sixteen columns coverPage">
   <p>
      Furls Crochet has several different yarn bowls to choose from, so 
      how do you know which one is best for you?
   </p>
   <p> 
      We've noticed that quite often our preferred home decor aesthetic carries over into all 
      aspects of our lives. Is this true for you, too? 
   </p>
   <p class="strong">
      Answer each question honestly by just going with your gut and 
      choosing the answers that are most appealing.
   </p>
  <br/>
   <span class="fakeButton">Start the quiz!</span><br>
  <img loading="lazy" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0166/0254/files/yarn-bowl-quiz-coverPage-banner_-_1.jpeg?v=1602264724">
</div>

<div class="sixteen columns">
  <!-- Buttons -->
  <div class="controls header">
      <button class="previous">Previous</button>
      <button class="next">Next</button>
  </div>
</div>

